<br>
Then I hear this voice unknown that said “Special delivery for Lexxii of the guild Midnight Council.”<br>
<br>
I joked “Another mammogram?”<br>
<br>
After sharing a laugh I discovered it was our GM Saviente and he was invisible. He gave me these. =)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://fantazone.com/mcresources/mantle.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
I was blushing bright blue.<br>
<br>
Now I ask you, with all the upbeat “Messages of the Day”, his humor, his attitude and then to take the time out of his busy Godly existence to visit (much less give someone flowers) Is he not just THE SWEETEST?<br>
Err ummm.. most EVIL in all the best ways?<br>
<br>
Twelve BLOOD red roses and thorns SOOOOOOOOOOO divine.<br>
<br>
As long as I exist they shall always rest with me right here.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://fantazone.com/mcresources/mantle2.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
I wanted to share these with you because we are a family. <br>
<br>
Magic? Oh yes, they sure put a smile on my evil lips. =) <br>
<br>
